PrecisEnactment of the FORMER MEMBERS OF PARLIAMENT ELECTIONS FOR JOINT AND SURVIVORS BENEFITS REGULATIONS which allow former Members of Parliament to elect to reduce their pensions in order to provide survivor benefits to a spouse who would not otherwise be entitled because they married after retirement.
